author: Lainey
text: It’s getting so close to my sisters 3 year passing & each day it starts to feel so much heavier than the last. Today all I keep thinking about is the ‘what if’s’. What if I didn’t go to work that day? What if ma & I got home even 10mins sooner? What if I loved her harder?
